title: MotoGP 14-CODEX
description:
CODEX PRESENTS:

                        MotoGP14 (c) Milestone S.r.l. 

    Release Date :  6/2014                         Protection : Steam
    Discs        :  1                              Genre      : Racing


  
    MotoGP14 is back with a comprehensively overhauled and improved
    graphics engine. New game modes, all the riders from the 2014 and
    2013 seasons and legendary riders from the history of the MotoGP
    give you the chance to live the dream of being a real rider.


    
   - Extract
   - Burn or mount the .iso
   - Run setup.exe and install 
   - Play 
   
      
   Block game exe in your firewall to prevent the game from trying to go 
   online ..
